    Top five birds counted yearly

    top_five_birds_yearly.Rd

    This function takes year as an input and allows user to view the top five birds counted in that year. It is also a parameterised version of the output of panel four of the shiny application of this package where the input "year" corresponds to the argument "num" in the function.

    Usage

    top_five_birds_yearly(num)

    Arguments

    num

    A numeric input of year between 1921 - 2017.
